title: Online Book Store
description: This Full-Stack app is forked from the original project collab. This forked version is with my local changes for the front end of the checkout page. This project helped me learn how to implement and connect flask to the front end to display the correct books in the checkout. Do not input your payment to web app. This is not a official book store.
techStackTitle: Javascript, CSS, HTML, Python, Flask, SQLite
